{"tid":756690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好多人冇搞清楚，香港跟本由一開始就唔屬於香港人","createTime":"2018-07-26T08:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T12:31:50.000Z","uid":22360,"like":10,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6ae98ff437c2032b897011f124c483cd766ea8ae","tid":756690,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:27:06.000Z","msg":"國際金融中心嘅意思，就係呢個地方係資本主義嘅大本營，而唔係香港人嘅土地。李嘉誠、李兆基亦唔係以香港人身份稱霸香港市場，而係以資本家身份。換成係白人黑人印度人，一樣可以以同樣方法剝削香港人（現在進行式）。<br />\n<br />\n由清朝割讓香港比英國開始，已經注定香港人嘅命運係無依無靠。由殖民時期開始，香港政府嘅任務已經唔係保護本地人利益，40年之後嘅移民更加唔洗討論。大部分香港人嘅角色，就係提供密集勞動嘅人力，我地可以留係香港，純粹係因為我地「湊巧」出生係香港，動員我地，比招外國勞工更方便，快捷，但一旦我地要求太多，「成本太高」，亦有一百種方法迫我地離開香港。<br />\n<br />\n指責大陸人，南亞人入侵香港，跟本係無稽之談，係典型嘅轉移矛盾。問題核心在於，我地以為趕走大陸人、南亞人，就可以重奪香港。然而事實上，只不過係重奪咗底層嘅位置。<br />\n<br />\n更何況，如果資本家想要南亞人多過香港人，我地只可以死撚開。"},{"pid":"34d7ba18a4305ad080e2b75687f7cdad9b572abb","tid":756690,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8858fb77f3d6dcb4f2c5cf64cb756570b46ad79","tid":756690,"uid":10692,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:31:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e289074cc7e39062f2c8a8754bd18fcb422efe9c","tid":756690,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34d7ba18a4305ad080e2b75687f7cdad9b572abb","tid":756690,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"佢意思係無香港人一說 香港人只係寄生係資本家底下嘅勞力 香港人同主子真正意思都係資本家 所以俾外族強姦只係奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791af8519be94d690488228c6f92e4c05420dd28","tid":756690,"uid":22360,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"嚴格黎講，「香港人」跟本不存在，從來唔係一個利益共同體。<br />\n<br />\n一個香港劏房戶同私樓戶嘅利益，比一個瑞士平民同瑞士總統嘅利益，前者更加矛盾、敵對。"},{"pid":"0bc83f2d81c94ce2606e53d4130062e8560472bb","tid":756690,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:40:46.000Z","msg":"幾時造反"},{"pid":"34c0d4ce4950eb6a2e508530e989c78cd3e8f2a6","tid":756690,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bc83f2d81c94ce2606e53d4130062e8560472bb","tid":756690,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:40:46.000Z","msg":"幾時造反"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:43:24.000Z","msg":"等你得閒"},{"pid":"26de2da8b5fa96a548d944131183c76bec329497","tid":756690,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:43:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b16dca2ff4cedc18f612e57c66be39b99edd0a86","tid":756690,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26de2da8b5fa96a548d944131183c76bec329497","tid":756690,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:43:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T09:17:57.000Z","msg":"香港人係近年先有既term"},{"pid":"91f6e04a4237493d9837382b31d573230638aef9","tid":756690,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T09:19:52.000Z","msg":"其實你想表達D乜"},{"pid":"200bda4ecf5f6aefca94c5bf458aa1341d3fabbd","tid":756690,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b16dca2ff4cedc18f612e57c66be39b99edd0a86","tid":756690,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26de2da8b5fa96a548d944131183c76bec329497","tid":756690,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:43:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T09:17:57.000Z","msg":"香港人係近年先有既term"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T09:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係掛, 近年先有"},{"pid":"ca0455cacee5137a3f58373614183e8d894bd121","tid":756690,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T09:24:10.000Z","msg":"真香港人有丁權<br />\n新香港人有大量資源<br />\n舊香港人有地產霸權<br />\n呢局打和<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0b1bc42fab81ec2d0f422eb56e55e318e11e04","tid":756690,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T12:31:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}